## Alert Triggers

The system automatically sends alerts for:

### Tunnel Alerts
| Condition | Severity | Channel | Rate Limit |
|-----------|----------|---------|------------|
| Agent offline > 5 min | High | Email, SMS | 5 min |
| Tunnel disconnected | High | Email, SMS | 5 min |
| All agents offline | Critical | Email, SMS, Webhook | 1 min |

### Agent Health Alerts
| Condition | Severity | Channel | Rate Limit |
|-----------|----------|---------|------------|
| Memory > 90% | High | Email | 5 min |
| Memory > 95% | Critical | Email, SMS | 2 min |
| CPU > 90% | High | Email | 5 min |
| CPU > 95% | Critical | Email, SMS | 2 min |
| Job failure rate > 30% | High | Email | 5 min |
| Job failure rate > 50% | Critical | Email, SMS | 2 min |

### Recovery Alerts
| Condition | Severity | Channel |
|-----------|----------|---------|
| Agent recovers after offline | Medium | Email |

