## Data Validation

All endpoints use Zod schemas defined in `lib/validations/health.ts`:

- `AgentHeartbeatSchema` - Full heartbeat payload
- `PingRequestSchema` - Ping request
- `ResourceMetricsSchema` - CPU, memory, disk, network
- `TunnelStatusSchema` - Tailscale connection status
- `AlertPayloadSchema` - Alert notification payload

Validation errors return 400 with detailed field errors.

