## Telemetry Store

In-memory store (`lib/store/telemetry-store.ts`) tracks:

- Agent heartbeats
- Response time history (last 100 samples)
- Consecutive failures
- First seen / last updated timestamps
- Tunnel status
- Resource metrics

**Methods:**
```typescript
telemetry.recordHeartbeat(agentId, heartbeat)
telemetry.recordPing(agentId, responseTimeMs)
telemetry.getAgent(agentId)
telemetry.getAllAgents()
telemetry.getAgentStatus(agentId)
telemetry.getAgentsByStatus(status)
telemetry.getOfflineAgents()
telemetry.getAverageResponseTime(agentId)
telemetry.getTunnelStatus(agentId)
telemetry.getResourceMetrics(agentId)
telemetry.getStats()
telemetry.checkOfflineAgents(thresholdMs)
telemetry.getCriticalHealthAgents()
```

