## Alerting Service

Alert routing service (`lib/services/alerting.ts`):

**Channels:**
- Email (Resend) - All severities
- SMS (Twilio) - High and Critical (stubbed)
- Webhook - Configurable endpoints

**Usage:**
```typescript
import { alerting } from "@/lib/services/alerting"

await alerting.sendAlert({
  severity: "high",
  category: "tunnel",
  title: "Agent offline",
  message: "Agent X has been offline for 5 minutes",
  agentId: "agent-001",
  agentName: "OpenClaw-Primary",
  timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
  requiresAck: true,
})
```

**Rate Limiting:**
- Low: 5 minutes
- Medium: 2 minutes
- High: 1 minute
- Critical: 30 seconds

